So, little theory, because why not

The girls are kind of escaping/ not doing the things they don't want to do.

Yuna is a model. She stands backstage, being uncomfortable with wearing heels, so she takes them of.
Lia lives in a golden cage, not being allowed to have fun, so she starts dancing on the table
Chaeryung works in a factory, where she is being watched. Eventually she is so scared that she runs away from the security cameras.
Ryujin seems to be in a bathroom of a club, so my guess is that she was maybe touched or catcalled, so she cuts her her (Symbolisme for feminisme)
Yeji looks like she's having fun in a club, i don't really have a theory for her.
